 - [OBS] screens 1-9,11 have no dead ends (local-only; deny paths advance with hints); camera optional, usage strings present (project.pbxproj:1451-1452,1489-1490).
 - [OBS] `MirrorConfiguration.currentBaseURL()` honors a UserDefaults override before prod URL (MirrorConfiguration.swift:7-9) — sweep QA devices for stale overrides.
